headline: EA SPORTS™ Madden NFL 26 Simulation Reveals Seattle Seahawks to Win Super Bowl LX
summary: REDWOOD CITY, Calif., February 02, 2026--EA SPORTS™ Madden NFL 26 today revealed its official Super Bowl LX Simulation, predicting the Seattle Seahawks to win 23-20, and giving fans an early look at how the biggest game of the year could unfold.

headline: Earnings To Watch: Electronic Arts (EA) Reports Q4 Results Tomorrow
